# Zhenni Wu

Zhenni Wu is a highly motivated, results-driven individual with great passion for technology, startups and entrepreneurship. She has a big heart for the humanities and believes each and every one of us is capable of making the world a better place through innovative ideas, inspiring others, and bringing enthusiasm to everything we do. Currently, Zhenni is a marketing advisor at PuppyGraph and has over a decade of experience in developer relations, product management, and marketing.
